Sabrina had 20 - 10 = <<20-10=10>>10 cookies left after giving 10 cookies to her brother.
Sabrina's mother gave her 10/2 = <<10/2=5>>5 cookies.
So, she had 10 + 5 = <<10+5=51>>51 cookies then.
She gave 51 x 2/3 = <<51*2/3=34>>34 cookies to her sister.
Therefore, she only has 51 - 34 = <<51-34=17>>17 cookies left.
#### 17
